skins.shipDescription: Prototype Bulin MKII. Can be used to limit break all Super Rare ships.
skins.selfIntroduction: Hahaha! It's your lucky day now that you've met me! We can purin together from this day forward! What for? To make everyone stronger, obviously! How do you purin? Like this! Purin~! Purin~!
skins.acquisition: Purin~! The herald of good fortune has arrived! Are you ready? Raise your hands and follow me... Purin~ purin~!
skins.login: Righty tighty, Lefty loosey, Stay calm and Purin on!
skins.details: Staring at me all day won't turn you into an expert!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Purin~! It's so big in here! There's so much room to run around!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Oh right, it's not my job to just run around, is it? Purin~!
skins.secretaryIdle3: Purin~? I'm too loud? Hmph, who cares what you think!
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Purin~ purin~! (Prototype Bulin MKII continues to spin faster)
